$ and $2\\leq k\\leq n$. The upper and lower\nbounds for $t(n,k,\\ell)$ are also obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 31 Jan 2015 19:17:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-03"}
